                  <interp inst="t16871207-2-crimeloc6" type="placeName" value="St. Botolph Bishopsgate"></interp>
                  <interp inst="t16871207-2-crimeloc6" type="type" value="crimeLocation"></interp>
                  <join result="offencePlace" targOrder="Y" targets="t16871207-2-off4 t16871207-2-crimeloc6"></join>: He coming into the said Emertons House to Drink, took his opportunity, and left a Pewter Tankard in the room of the other; biding them take care of their Tankerd for which Exchange (contrary to the old Proverb) he was found <rs id="t16871207-2-verdict7" type="verdictDescription">
                     <interp inst="t16871207-2-verdict7" type="verdictCategory" value="guilty"></interp>
               guilty
            </rs> of the Felony.</p>
